        <p class="mt-3 text-xl text-white">We're committed to bring you the upmost quality with this new collection: Retro Style.
        </p>
        <a href="/products" class="transition ease-in-out delay-150 bg-orange-600 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-orange-500 duration-300 mt-8 w-full block border border-transparent rounded-md py-3 px-8 text-base font-medium text-white sm:w-auto">Browse Collection</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

